Template: tunneler-client/server_url
Type: string
Default: example.com
Description: Tunneler server address (domain or IP)
Description-ko.UTF-8: Tunneler 서버 주소 (도메인 또는 IP)

Template: tunneler-client/use_ssl
Type: boolean
Default: false
Description: Use SSL (HTTPS/WSS)?
Description-ko.UTF-8: SSL(HTTPS/WSS)을 사용합니까?

Template: tunneler-client/subdomain
Type: string
Description: Subdomain to use (for example: mybox)
Description-ko.UTF-8: 사용할 서브도메인 (예: mybox)

Template: tunneler-client/token
Type: string
Description: Authentication token (leave empty if unused)
Description-ko.UTF-8: 인증 토큰 (없으면 비워두세요)

Template: tunneler-client/http_base
Type: string
Description: Local HTTP base (for example: http://127.0.0.1:8000, leave empty if unused)
Description-ko.UTF-8: 로컬 HTTP 베이스 (예: http://127.0.0.1:8000, 없으면 비워두세요)

Template: tunneler-client/tcp_maps
Type: string
Description: TCP mappings (for example: ssh=127.0.0.1:22,db=127.0.0.1:5432)
Description-ko.UTF-8: TCP 매핑 (예: ssh=127.0.0.1:22,db=127.0.0.1:5432)

Template: tunneler-client/udp_maps
Type: string
Description: UDP mappings (for example: dns=127.0.0.1:53)
Description-ko.UTF-8: UDP 매핑 (예: dns=127.0.0.1:53)
